<topic id="apply-transformation-scenarios">
  <title>Applying Associated Transformation Scenarios</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Transformation Scenarios<indexterm>Apply transformation
          scenarios</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>If you have associated transformation scenarios for the current document (in the <xref
        href="configure-transformation-dialog.dita#configure-transformation-dialog"
          ><uicontrol>Configure Transformation Scenario(s)</uicontrol> dialog box</xref> or <xref
        href="scenarios-view.dita#scenarios-view"><b>Transformation Scenarios</b> view</xref>), <ph
        keyref="product"/> included an <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png"/>Apply
        Transformation Scenario(s)</uicontrol> action that allows you to quickly apply the
      associated transformation scenarios on the current document. Note that if an association is
      not detected, this action will open the <xref
        href="configure-transformation-dialog.dita#configure-transformation-dialog"
          ><uicontrol>Configure Transformation Scenario(s)</uicontrol> dialog box</xref> where you
      can choose the scenarios you want to apply.</p>
    <p>The <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png"/>Apply Transformation
        Scenario(s)</uicontrol> action can be initiated from any of the following methods:<ul>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol><shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_shift_t_shortcut"
              product="author developer editor"/></uicontrol><uicontrol><shortcut
              conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/alt_shift_tt_shortcut"
              product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"/>)</uicontrol> keyboard
          shortcut.</li>
        <li>Click the <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png"/>Apply Transformation
            Scenario(s)</uicontrol> button on the main toolbar.</li>
        <li>Click the <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png"/>Apply Transformation
            Scenario(s)</uicontrol> button on the toolbar in the <xref
            href="scenarios-view.dita#scenarios-view"><b>Transformation Scenarios</b>
          view</xref>.</li>
        <li>Right-click a file in the <xref
            href="using-the-project-view.dita#using-the-project-view"><uicontrol
              product="author developer editor">Project</uicontrol><uicontrol
              product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Project Explorer</uicontrol>
            view</xref> and select <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Transform</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol><image href="../img/ApplyStyleSheet16.png"/>Apply Transformation
              Scenario(s)</uicontrol>
          </menucascade>.</li>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol>Apply Associated</uicontrol> button in the <xref
            href="configure-transformation-dialog.dita#configure-transformation-dialog"
              ><uicontrol>Configure Transformation Scenario(s)</uicontrol> dialog box</xref>.</li>
      </ul></p>
